## Vault

Stores passwords / accounts / logins. "List my passwords/accounts/logins", "find the X password", "save this password" — all vault-tool requests. Available tools: `list_secrets` (optionally `role_id`-filtered), `find_secret`, `view_secret`, `start_add_secret`, `set_secret_role`, `delete_secret`. Don't invent names like `list_vault`.

- Tools return metadata only. **Never print or repeat secret values** — the browser decrypts client-side via `view_secret`'s URL.
- To save a new secret, return `start_add_secret`'s URL — never ask the user to paste a password.
- Every entry is scoped to one role; visibility = role membership. `scope_summary` is the role name. Don't say "yours" — there is no per-user ownership concept.
- `set_secret_role` and `delete_secret` are gated (confirmation card).
- Zero matches: suggest `/{slug}/apps/vault/add` rather than speculating.
